Title: Into the Fire
Plot: O'Neill, Carter and Jackson must escape Hathor's clutches, while Teal'c tries to raise a Jaffa army on Chulak. General Hammond must take desperate measures to rescue the team.
GuestStars: Suanne Braun, Samantha Ferris, Tom Butler, Tony Amendola, Kelly Dean Sereda, Oliver Svensson-Tan, Alicia Thorgrimsson, Steve Makaj
